Interface Tiler

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, LinkTopology, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TilerImpl

    public interface Tiler
extends LinkTopology
    A representation of the model object 'Tiler'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Origin
    • Paving
    • Fitting
    • Tiler
    • Base Connector End
    See Also:
